{"tid":974563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每個連登仔心入面都有一個林子健","createTime":"2019-01-09T03:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T15:10:41.000Z","uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e593c4527767a150a9762419abc453e92625264","tid":974563,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:49:14.000Z","msg":"每個連登仔心入面有一個，或者係一個林子健。<br />\n<br />\n林子健同大多數連登仔衣著同樣貌相近。<br />\n被泛民放棄成為棄卒，但佢無放棄。<br />\n爭取住連登仔心目中嘅正義。<br />\n雖然受千夫所指，但佢企出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林子健代表住連登仔嘅正義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家有危險，佢需要連登仔嘅支持。"},{"pid":"70a7dee793fbd76df0a594c5704b1d4795f63a7a","tid":974563,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03990f8caa357cef36ed3d3228036bc58c0afa25","tid":974563,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"今天，我們都是林子健"},{"pid":"327bc68c38684a5111b211644d8b324780dc03e2","tid":974563,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"做埋d 自編自導既on9野"},{"pid":"a1909f0f96e0b9ab0f38009b6dc395c6c51bd37a","tid":974563,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03990f8caa357cef36ed3d3228036bc58c0afa25","tid":974563,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"今天，我們都是林子健"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"24c10b9ae23f3efeefc77bfb3a3bae6057ab132d","tid":974563,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"連登為正義，請企出嚟"}]}